name: Tether USD Bridged GEN Z (USDT.z)
description: Tether USD Bridged GEN Z (USDT.z) is an ERC-20 stablecoin deployed on Ethereum, built to deliver consistency, seamless connectivity, and functional tools in the expanding blockchain space. Linked 1:1 to the US Dollar through reserves, USDT.z counters crypto market instability, facilitating dependable payments, global remittances, and DeFi engagements without borders.
